{
 "name": "RPlog_Ritual_of_Darkness",
 "title": "Ritual of Darkness",
 "summary": "In the ancient Massassi Temple amid the jungle wilderness of Yavin, a host of Force users gathers as a dark ritual unfolds. The Jedi and adepts Aurejin, Jessalyn Valios, Mailyn Raines, Markus, Mira, and Simon Sezirok converge with others -- the captive Kyokusha, Jarin, and Kyo -- under the looming menace of the Sith Lord Valak. As the diffused orange light filters through the Grand Audience Chamber's slanted skylights, the rite of darkness draws the participants into a perilous confrontation between the light and the dark side. The multi-part scene chronicles the harrowing ritual and the clash of wills it provokes within the Massassi temple.",
